{"type": "article", "id": 18051, "title": "异地情侣想要拉近距离，不如一起搞个小艺术项目", "description": "不过话说回来，有搞艺术项目的心，也不太会生分吧。", "date": "2015-11-25T19:15:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 19299, "name": "情侣"}, {"id": 19300, "name": "艺术项目"}, {"id": 153, "name": "摄影"}, {"id": 296, "name": "自拍"}, {"id": 26, "name": "instagram"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 149, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606152022HaAGPcnUTFpW65hb.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t只要高兴，情侣们随时都可以虐狗，比如下面这对儿韩国情侣。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t女孩叫 <span>Danbi Shin </span>，常住纽约，男孩叫 <span>Seok Li</span>，住在首尔。为了拉近两人间的距离，<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/shinliart/\" target=\"_blank\">他们在 Instagram 上做了一个摄影项目</a>，叫作 <a href=\"http://mashable.com/2015/11/19/couple-long-distance-relationship-photos/#xBarN6qAGmqZ\" target=\"_blank\">Half &amp; Half</a>，在这个项目里，所有的照片都是两张图拼起来的——拉面、广告牌、垃圾桶、自拍脸，纽约和首尔一半一半。一边谈恋爱一边搞艺术，或许真是拉近距离的好方法呢。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152014fHnZVwNsq7KeRQ0P.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.99777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152015OMnkQHFUZrv0ct1E.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.99019608\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152015YfOC32cXtbdQyFzs.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.99511002\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152016iOhkfGZvFrcymENd.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.99513382\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152016IcVWMKnQbJSUTPCd.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.98543689\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152017QYDXb7Ts9x5u3yfG.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.98058252\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152017LvAYPy8rEFzwWaTf.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.98547215\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152018Zc6phyAgN4P90tsq.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.99266504\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152018lr3cQOjFB9D5k4I7.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.99270073\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152019iAsPQqOCJt958EDe.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"1.0122549\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152019sLRFd4ijVNgG5f9w.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.997543\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061520203j9rwqZuaPC2kzWc.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.99509804\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152020g2Tuknxso85a0PG6.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.99019608\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152021hpdSHe41U3iu5Isa.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.98288509\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152021t03m1TxhbZV2XEpk.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.99512195\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152022mdRCry7UvaQucNhL.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.99754902\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这些照片说简单也简单，说难也难。饭盒、叉子很好拍，把它们平放即可，可以一人先拍，另外一人照着已有照片找角度。但若想把<span>广告牌和建筑物</span>拼凑的那么完整，还真得有些技巧——情侣们要熟练掌握三脚架、PS 和沟通技巧。目前，他们的 Instagram 账号还在持续更新中，已有超过 9 万人关注。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t题图来源：<a href=\"http://mashable.com/2015/11/19/couple-long-distance-relationship-photos/#xBarN6qAGmqZ\" target=\"_blank\">mashable</a> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}